Package modalLogic.formula

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constant  
    Formula<T>
    Abstract class Formula, represents a (modal) logic formula (if root node) or subformula (if inner node) as a tree.
    FormulaImpl<T>
    Class FormulaImpl provides an implementation of the inner nodes of the formula tree.
    Literal<T>
    Class Literal provides the leafs of the formula tree.
    ParentDisj<P>
    Class ParentDisj provides methods to traverse a formulas parent disjunctions.
